manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.lightcone.vlogstar.homepage.MainActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

playstore_details.description:
Film Maker is the best video editor & free video maker made for both professionals and amateurs. We have the most useful video editing features that other top pro video editor and slideshow maker app have, but more convenient to edit and professional to display.

Create Hollywood-style movies of great power like a pro director, and share to Instagram, Tik Tok, Youtube, WhatsApp & other social media! The power of this video editor won't disappoint you.

Film Maker Features:

● Free Video Editor & Video Maker:
Everyone can be a pro director of great power using Film Maker editing features like trim, split, cut, duplicate & detach audio from videos. 
Share and show your video with friends after youcut. 

● Free Video Intro Templates:
With our FREE, no crop, well-designed intro templates, you can easily create intro for your video and for your YouTube channel. Add texts, emojis, stickers, music, sound effects the way you like. Video outro templates will soon be available, too.

● Video Filters & Video Transition:
Movie, retro, selfie, and 50 other fabulous filters available for you to choose. 
30+ transitions to be added between video clips. 

● FX Video Editor & Merger:
Edit videos with 100+ featured effects including VHS and Glitch. 
Use this video maker with special glitch effects to get tons of likes on Instagram and Tik Tok! 

● Music Video Editor & Cropper:
Make a rhythmic video with 100+ FREE featured music. 
Add narration and voice-over to your video. 
Adjust volume, speed, fade in and fade out or trim in this video maker. 

● Pro Video Trimmer, Cutter & Video Joiner:
Merge video clips into one video. It is a pocket video editor and movie maker which helps rotate video and crop video, compress and combine videos without losing quality. 

● Blur Video Editor:
Create blur backgrounds for your videos and photos or add blur directly. 
FREE blur video editor app that can adjust the blur level at will. 
Add featured colors and video fade to your vlog video background. 
More adjustable parameters include brightness, exposure, contrast, shadow.

● Funny Video Editor & Cutter:
Hundreds of popular stickers, funny emoji, animated stickers, illustrations and more. 
100+ Featured sound effects like animals, explosions, laughter. 
Make fun videos that make people laugh! 

● Text on Video Editor:
Hundreds of well-designed fonts. 
Freely add various text, dynamic FX text, design text and movie subtitles. Make your pictures & videos stand out with well-designed animated hype type text. 

● Video Speed Control:
Adjust video & music speed precisely. 
Create slow motion & fast motion playback and reverse videos to present stunning cinematic time-lapse effects. 

● Blending Modes:
Use the professional blending modes to create excellent double exposures: multiply, screen, overlay, etc.

● Multiple Layers Video Splitter:
Multiple layers of text, music, images, stickers, special effects and doodle. 
A perfect video editor for making slideshows. 
Merge clips into one with different options in this video joiner & movie maker. 

● Video Compressor & Converter:
Save videos from this video maker & upload to YouTube, Facebook, WhatsApp & more. 
Share your final cut from this video editor with friends on social media. 
Free to export video in 720p, Full HD 1080p with no quality loss. 

Use this pocket video editing movie master, mv master & video maker to edit videos, make lumafusion, quickshot, intro, outro, films and movies and make final cut like a pro kinemaster. To be the shiniest pocket video star and the best videoshop in getting pro filmic videos as a movie maker. Alight your motion graphics to make a videoleap towards professional-quality animation.

If you are using a device equipped with powerful video decoding functionalities, you will have a better and smoother video editing experience in Film Maker. 

If you need our help with any issues, please email us at cerdillaczhang@outlook.com. We'll get back to you as soon as possible.
